        '''With the advent of T20 Internationals and the shorter formats gaining popularity - aggressive batting is an essential part of every budding batter's arsenal. An important aspect of a high-scoring batsman's game is bat speed. This is one of the factors that directly determine how far and how quickly a ball will travel after meeting the bat. There has been extensive research on power hitting and bat speed has come out as a major factor.

